Package PIM

Interface MicroserviceArchitecture

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface MicroserviceArchitecture extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Microservice Architecture'.

The following features are supported:

  • Architecture Name
  • Microservices
  • Generating PSM
